  "texts": [
    "It should be noted that ML systems do not operate on programmed solution algorithms but build a model themselves by learning from the available data.",
    "Machine learning algorithms ensure that the results of actions or changes in environmental conditions are used to optimise the system's performance in an iterative process.",
    "Hence, models based on machine learning must be trained and tested with given data sets before they can reasonably be used to draw conclusions from new data.",
    "ML is applied in many fields such as speech, image or natural language recognition.",
    "It may also be integrated into robotics, smart factories or smart home applications."
  ],
